AGI - Throughout his life he drove without ever getting his driver's license. A 83-year-old pensioner was discovered in Nuorese by the Bitti Polstrada, who had stopped him for a control while riding a scooter.
&nbsp;
To the agents the man explained that he did not believe it was necessary to drive vehicles of low capacity and confided to have done it for decades, throughout the Nuorese, without anyone ever stopping it or questioning him any. This time, however, the pensioner was sanctioned and the scooter stop was taken.
